data.description: ***Open House this Sunday, October 15th 11am -3pm***Welcome to 232 Wickersham! Your new home sitting on a quiet cul-de-sac in the lovely Boerne community, Southglen. Approaching the house you will see an inviting front porch with an updated front door. As you walk inside you will be greeted with a formal dining area with plenty of natural light shining through a modern style window formation! Entering into the kitchen you will fall in love with the gray cabinets and white quartzite counter tops. Then fall in love all over again imagining your family gathered around the white quartzite island in the middle of the kitchen. To the left is a little nook with built in desk and cabinets. Built to perfection for all your kids homework and craft needs! This is the open floor plan you have always dreamed of as you can make your way right into the living room with plenty of space to do activities! The master bedroom is a big space that give you plenty of room for that King size bed and furniture. Master bath provides a garden tub and a giant shower! Upstairs you will find family room and a bonus media room! Along with the 3 secondary bedrooms! This energy efficient home (solar panels) is waiting for it's new owners! This is the house to make memories for years to come!***SOLAR PANELS,REFRIGERATOR, WASHER AND DRYER, AND WATER SOFTENER CONVEY WITH THE HOUSE!***
